description:
One might wonder why a 23- year-old-man would want to play every educational Sonic game, but the truth is, my math, reading, and spelling skills are that of an unborn-child. Long story short, I have to play these games to get my high-school diploma. NOTE: No copies of Sonic's Schoolhouse were harmed in the making of this video.
